oakley® and vicis launch advanced eye shield for the zero football helmet oakley® and vicis launch advanced eye shield for the zero football helmet the best helmet in the world just got better with the highestperforming football shield ever developed news provided by vicis inc  oakley inc jul    et share this article foothill ranch calif july   prnewswire  today oakley® and vicis announced the launch of the vicis edge shield™ by oakley developed exclusively for vicis zero engineered to enhance performance and optimize safety the edge shield is the first ever codeveloped football optics system oakley logo vicis oakley prizm shield looking to complete the most technologically advanced football helmet ever designed vicis sought out a leader in the optics industry oakley the two brands both built on innovation and sports performance collaborated on research and development adding oakleys leading performance innovations and quality optics to zero a highly engineered football helmet that earned the top rank in  nflnflpa tests rooted in oakleys year history in innovation and rigorous safety tests that set the brand apart the vicis edge shield by oakley is designed to complement the wide field of view of the zero and improve clarity and contrast for the player leveraging new manufacturing tools and software including a new freeform approach to high definition optics® hdo the edge shield by oakley was exclusively engineered for zero allowing the brand to create an optically correct shield to match the unique shape of zero facemasks the zero offers the widest field of view of any football helmet on the market – nearly the limit of human peripheral vision oakleys collaboration with vicis is a testament to the brands belief that everything can and will be made better said ryan saylor oakley vice president of advanced product development extending our leading optics technology to another field allowed us to create the highest performance football shield for the highest performance helmet we are excited to see the impact that it will have on the game of football and athletes performance and safety the vicis edge shield by oakley will be the only football shield available with oakley prizm™ a revolutionary lens technology that has turned eyewear into vital equipment for sports prizm is engineered to dramatically enhance detail and help improve performance by providing ultraprecise color tuning designed for specific environments the vicis edge shield by oakley is molded out of oakleys high impact plutonite® a proprietary synthetic material that blocks  of harmful uv rays and helps protect athletes eyes during games and training we saw an opportunity to partner with oakley to help players elevate their performance via improved optics said dave marver vicis ceo and cofounder our goal is that athletes wearing a zero will benefit from industry leading field of view enhanced optical clarity and better protection the vicis edge shield by oakley will be offered in prizm and nonprizm configurations in september  the vicis edge shield by oakley will be distributed by vicis directly to teams and can be ordered online at wwwvicisco to learn more about oakleys prizm lens technology please visit oakleycomprizm discover more twitter oakley vicisproinstagram oakley vicisprofacebook facebookcomoakley facebookcomvicispro   about oakley inc established in  and headquartered in southern california oakley is one of the leading product design and sport performance brands in the world the holder of more than  patents oakley is a culture of creators inventors idealists and scientists obsessed with using design and innovation to create products and experiences that inspire greatness this philosophy has made oakley one of the most iconic and inimitable brands on the market with products that worldclass athletes around the globe depend on to compete at the highest level possible oakley is known for its high definition optics® which features unparalleled optical clarity and precision along with impact resistance and uv protection incorporated into all of the brands sun prescription eyewear and premium goggles oakley extended its position as the worlds leading sports eyewear brand into apparel and accessories oakley has mens and womens product lines that appeal to sports performance active and lifestyle consumers oakley is a subsidiary of luxottica group additional information is available at httpwwwoakleycom oakley® high definition optics® and plutonite® are registered trademarks of oakley inc about vicis headquartered in seattle vicis is a sports technology company focused on developing a highly engineered football helmet to improve protection and performance vicis flagship helmet the zero was shaped by some of the worlds leading athletes engineers and neurosurgeons and ranked first in the  nflnflpa helmet laboratory performance testing vicis is funded by several prominent spine and neurological surgeons current and former nfl players harry fath the peregrine group angelmd w fund alliance of angels and trilogy equity partners for more information please visit httpwwwvicisco copyright  oakley inc all rights reserved   view original content with multimediahttpwwwprnewswirecomnewsreleasesoakleyandvicislaunchadvancedeyeshieldforthezerofootballhelmethtml source vicis inc oakley inc related links httpwwwvicisco my news release contains wide tables view fullscreen you just read oakley® and vicis launch advanced eye shield for the zero football helmet news provided by vicis inc  oakley inc jul    et share this article looking to send a news release with pr newswire take advantage of the worlds leading distribution platform sign up to get started request more information have an account log in search searching for your content advanced search vicis inc private company information  bloomberg july    am et leisure products company overview of vicis inc snapshot people company overview vicis inc designs and manufactures football helmets tha