ovide resources for personal and professional development amongst the football coaching profession aema the purpose of the the athletic equipment managers association aema is to promote advance and improve the equipment managers profession in all of its many phases one goal is to work as a group to bring about equipment improvements for the greater safety of all participants in sports and recreation nata the national athletic trainers’ association nata is the professional membership association for certified athletic trainers and others who support the athletic training profession the mission of the nata is to represent engage and foster the continued growth and development of the athletic training profession and athletic trainers as unique health care providers sfia the sports  fitness industry association sfia is the trade association of leading industry sports and fitness brands suppliers retailers and partners their mission is to “promote sports and fitness participation and industry vitality” by focusing on core product areas for the industry nsga the national sporting goods association nsga is a nonprofit trade association that provides information to and advocates for the sporting goods industry the nsga supports its members’ efforts to grow the business and advocates on their behalf processing thank you your subscription has been confirmed youll hear from us soon errorhere contact vicis headquarters in seattle zero about zero® axis fit system® cleaning and maintenance about council team partners clinic iisa vicis foundation coalition devblog media press awards videos images sign up × sign up for vicis email with vicis huddle you can be the first to know about product releases development advancements and other vicis news email name add me to the waitlist to purchase a zero when available placeholder sign up contact us want to know more let us know how we can keep you up to date be sure to use the drop down menu to tell us about yourself so we can send you th