ta does not yet exist to support such a claim enjoy the articles and please register on our contact page to follow our progress  for media inquiries please contact vicisbarokascom  the quest for a better football helmetmay   vicis looking to make its mark with helmets in nflmay   the safest helmet in football is set to make its nfl debut next seasonmay   the football helmet just got the biggest redesign since the sand its coming to the nfl next seasonmay   vicis helmets to be tested in spring collegiate and professional football gamesapril   nfl and ncaa teams will equip players with vicis hightech helmets during spring footballapril   these companies are using tech to tackle football’s concussion conundrumjanuary   vicis partners with university of alabama at birmingham to create ‘next generation’ football helmetsjanuary   can this helmet make football saferseptember   reimaging the football helmet for safetyseptember   footballs endgame what would happen if americas pastime just  diedaugust   vicis and the national football foundation announce new sponsorshipaugust   soft helmet to debut in nfl this fallaugust   saints hc sean payton talks about the coming innovation in helmetsapril   how this seattle startup created the helmet that could save footballfebruary   can this new football helmet prevent head injuriesfebruary   headline experimental helmet aims to fix footballfebruary   this helmet crumples  and that’s goodjanuary   the inside out football helmet that crumples radical design that could reduce brain traumajanuary   the zero flexible football helmet may save players’ brainsjanuary   rethinking the nextgeneration helmetdecember   concussions and the future of the nfldecember   how do you solve a problem like concussions in youth sportsdecember   uw vicis again recognized for innovative helmet researchdecember   nfl invests m in concussion preventiondecember   nfl investing m in new technology to prevent concussionsdecember   uw medicine teams up with nfl o