 invest as a physicianphysicianregister your startup to be listed on angelmd applying for funding is optionalstartupif you are a physician and you want to register your medical startup start by registering your startup we will follow up to provide your investing credentials separatelyplease crop the photodonecancelvicis incvicis inc is developing a novel helmet technology to reduce risk of from head impacts beginning with a football helmetof the story   americans love football but sportsrelated head injury is a widespread and increasing concern at all levels of the game  current football helmets do an effective job protecting against skull fracture but they are not designed to reduce risk of traumatic brain injury we’ve completely reimagined the football helmet leveraging contributions thoughtleading neurological surgeons and mechanical engineers the result is a product that is performing exceptionally well vs current marketleading helmets in industrystandard impact tests  these data obtained from independent labs suggest our helmet will significantly reduce impact forces in addition to emphasizing safety we have put great focus on fit comfort performance and design this will be a helmet players love to wear we are starting with football but will expand into other contact sports we have attracted a worldclass group of scientific and athletic advisors  our scientific advisors include three members of the nfl head neck and spine committee including a cochair  our athletic advisors include two nfl hall of fame inductees and several super bowl champions we have raised m in grant and investment funding to date including a grant from the nfl ge and under armour as part of the head health challenge ii initiative investors include peregrine group trilogy equity partners angelmd wfund alliance of angels and a number of individual investors whose ranks include neurosurgeons spine surgeons attorneys and current and former nfl players and coaches we are currently filling a convertible note the helmet industry has been slow to innovate  that needs to change  we are driven to make a profound difference by making the game safer for athletes of all ages  we welcome your support for our initiative       vicis inc mercer street seattle wa united statesjoinorloginto view the full profile meet the team get updates news and investment details or connect with this or any company on the networklearn moremapokcloseengaging as an would you like us to send a message to this startups management team requesting information on becoming an yesnoverify your account  step thank you for registeringverify your account  step we have sent you an email to verify your account click on the angelmd link to complete your registrationif you have questions please contact us at infoangelmdcoif you are having trouble or would like to contact us please fill out a support ticket by clicking hereokprivacy policyrespecting privacy and confidentiality is a top priority for angelmd we respect the trust you place in us and the confidential nature of the information you provide through your relationship with us except as you may otherwise expressly approve we limit the collection and use of client and user information to what we believe would be useful to service your accounts administer our business or tell you about our serviceswe restrict employee access to client and user information to those who need to know in order to provide services to you we maintain appropriate security standards and procedures to protect information about you and we will respond quickly to your request to correct inaccurate informationin the event of a revision to this privacy policy the revised version will be posted on the angelmd sitewe only use your information as appropriate to provide you with quality services and to ensure security for example we may use the information collected from you to verify your identity and contact informationif at any time you choose to purchase a product or service 